file_content.text: Warning: Cryonics systems offline. Experimental specimens have been released.
Cryonics power failure. Experimental specimens awakening.
Warning: Life support systems damaged. Oxygen depletion in progress.
Power fluctuations detected in electrical conduits. Conduits may become unstable; caution is advised.
Warning: Secondary power systems damaged. Nonessential systems may be inoperable.
Additional security forces are needed in the cargo area to enforce containment measures. Please respond.
